This directory contains the LLF implementation of cut elimination
for first-order linear hereditary Harrop formulas described for
example in 

  Joshua Hodas and Dale Miller: "Logic Programming in a Fragment of
  Intuitionistic Linear Logic".  Information and Computation
  110(2):327-355, 1994.

The encoding is analyzed at length in

  Iliano Cervesato: "A Linear Logical Framework", Ph. D. thesis,
  Department of Computer Science, University of Turin, Italy.
  English version to appear shortly.